long_desc.thetext: Patch for dialog trunk version which allow to place the dialog near the widget which trigger it. I change also the demo application to place dialogues near buttons. All dialogues worked except form dialog (don't understand why).
Hi, there is no patch attached to this bug. Please add it. However, if the patch breaks the demo, I cannot apply it, sorry. I'll have a look if I can find out what the problem is.

Created attachment 1088 Dialog trunk version with optional parameter: place to widget
In this patch I just change dialog.Dialog class (source), to have one more property: the widget. This property is null by default. If it's not set the dialog is placed to center. The actual demo works with this patch, but you can't test the effect of this change. So in this patch I also change the demo, to pass the trigger button as parameter and place the dialog close to it.
